description: Theta series of 4-dimensional lattice A_2 tensor A2, with det 81, minimal norm 4.
formula: After rescaling, this is equal to (theta series of A2)^2 + 2*(theta series of A_2 with respect to deep hole)^2, i.e. J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. 111, Eq. (60)^2 + 2*Eq.(63)^2.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
